        What Happens if Your Brisbane Property Is Damaged Between Exchange and Settlement
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Queensland's rules on who bears responsibility for property damage after exchange are not what most sellers expect. Understanding your obligations before something goes wrong is considerably better than learning them after.
      </p>
